@j1337-l1n, They are still fans. Just like there are people that don’t like carrots or the color red. Fans are allowed to have their own opinions. 

I do wish that hurtful comments are restrained, but that is on the person making those comments. You label them toxic allows you to dismiss them as a person. Also, the child actor could have simply not been on the internet to see those messages. My wife doesn’t have any social media presence. The parents, agent, and child actor should have simply avoided it.

There are 8 billion people on planet earth. Each one is entitled to their opinion. You are also entitled to not listen to them.
